      <!-- Get Involved -->
      <mj-wrapper background-color="#f5f5f5" padding="15 0" css-class="blue">
        <mj-section padding="10 0" background-color="#218fff" border-radius="3">
          <mj-column>
            <mj-text align="left" font-size="20" color="#FFF" font-weight="700" padding-bottom="0">
              Get Involved
            </mj-text>

            <mj-text align="left" font-size="14" color="#FFF" font-weight="400" padding-top="0">
              <p style="color:#fff;">
                As we mentioned on last week’s membership call, our work is far from done. This month we are launching several exciting new campaigns, and we need you to join us. Below is information for each of these initiatives and how you can get involved:

              </p>
              <ul style="color:#fff;">
                <li>
                  <a href="http://fightforourdream.com?source=em171129" style="color:#fff;" target="_blank">#OurDream</a> - In the aftermath of President Trump's repeal of the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals, otherwise known as DACA, undocumented
                  youth and Dreamers are leading the campaign to pass a clean DREAM Act in Congress. To get involved visit our <a href="http://fightforourdream.com?source=em171129" style="color:#fff;" target="_blank">website</a>.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="https://go.ourrevolution.com/page/content/tax-plan/?source=em171129" style="color:#fff;" target="_blank">The Republican's Tax Reform Plan</a> - The Republicans are doing everything in their power to push through a tax plan that
                  offers massive tax breaks to corporations and the wealthy. This plan does nothing for the middle class and working families, in fact, anyone making more than $75,000 annually will see an increase in their taxes by 2027. <a href="https://go.ourrevolution.com/page/content/tax-plan/?source=em171129"
                    style="color:#fff;" target="_blank">We must fight back</a>.

                </li>
                <li>
                  Learn how to broadcast and record meetings and events using Uphill Media to support local candidates, organize, and grow your group. Get started at <a href="https://www.uphillmedia.org/work-with-us.html" style="color:#fff;" target="_blank">uphillmedia.org</a>.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
        </mj-section>
      </mj-wrapper>

      <!-- A New Generation of Progressive Leaders -->
      <mj-wrapper padding="0 0 15">
        <mj-section padding="10 0" background-color="#fff" border-radius="3">
          <mj-column>
            <mj-text align="left" font-size="20" color="#4A4A4A" font-weight="700" padding-bottom="0">
              A New Generation of Progressive Leaders
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" font-size="14" color="#4A4A4A" font-weight="400" padding-top="0" padding-bottom="0">
              <p>
                November has been a historic month for Our Revolution. Alongside local groups and volunteers across the country, we worked to elect a new generation of progressive leaders.
              </p>
              <p>
                Twenty-seven Our Revolution endorsed candidates won their elections and brought the political revolution to almost every corner of the United States. In Virginia, Lee Carter defeated Virginia’s GOP Majority Whip by over 1,500 votes and Elizabeth Guzman
                became one of the first Latinas elected to Virginia’s House of Delegates. In Minnesota, Andrea Jenkins became the first out transgender woman elected to Minneapolis City Council. In Maine, for the first time ever, voters passed a ballot
                measure to expand Medicaid.
              </p>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
        </mj-section>
      </mj-wrapper>

