            </mj-text>
            <mj-image padding="0" src="https://s.bsd.net/ourrev/main/page/-/images/newsletter/or-somerville.jpg"></mj-image>
            <mj-text font-size="12" font-style="italic">Our Revolution Somerville</mj-text>
