      <!-- Every Vote Counts -->
      <mj-wrapper padding="0 0 15">
        <mj-section padding="10 0" background-color="#fff" border-radius="3">
          <mj-column>
            <mj-text align="left" font-size="20" color="#4A4A4A" font-weight="700" padding-bottom="0">
              Every Vote Counts
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" font-size="14" color="#4A4A4A" font-weight="400" padding-top="0" padding-bottom="0">
              <p>
                Local groups, State Organizing Committees, and distributed volunteers worked in tandem to ensure every voter knew their polling place, voting hours, and who was on their ballot. <strong>Our Revolution’s amazing volunteers across the country put in countless hours
                during the November election cycle to make over 132,000 calls and send over 373,000 individual text messages.</strong> Thousands of voters got out and voted because of the hard work and dedication of Our Revolution’s volunteers - thank
                you for all that you do.
              </p>
              <p>
                We have seen the direct results of the hard work of our volunteers and Our Revolution groups across the country, especially in the races won by tight margins. Here are just a few of the Our Revolution endorsed candidates who won by less than 1,000 votes:
              </p>
