      <!-- Win or Lose -->
      <mj-wrapper background-color="#f5f5f5" padding="0 0 15 0" css-class="blue">
        <mj-section padding="10 0" background-color="#218fff" border-radius="3">
          <mj-column>
            <mj-text align="left" font-size="20" color="#FFF" font-weight="700" padding-bottom="0">
              Win or Lose
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" font-size="14" color="#FFF" font-weight="400" padding-top="0">
              <p style="color:#fff;">
                <em>“We are building sustainable grassroots power in communities, win or lose.”</em><br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&mdash; David Lynch, Our Revolution Volunteer
              </p>
              <p style="color:#fff;">
                Not all victories are appropriately measured just by the results on election night. So many of our candidates created real grassroots movements in their communities by introducing new ideas and providing voters with an alternative to establishment politicians.
                These movements are pivotal to long-term change. Win or lose, the progress we have made this year is ground-breaking. Together we will continue to work to create a political revolution that will last and create needed change for all.
              </p>
              </p>
            </mj-text>
